Usage:
        #ban <cn> [time [m|h]] [reason]
Author:
        SuckerServ / HopMod
Description:
        With this command you can kick and ban a player for the specified reason for the setted time.
Examples:
        #ban 2 1 h "A b C"      Kicks and bans the client with the clientnum 2 for 1 hour with reason "A b C".